      • setDelimiter

        public void setDelimiter(String delimiter)
        Sets the delimiter for list request.

        When set, the list request rolls up the results using the specified delimiter. The returned list contains:

      • unique object names up-to (and including) the delimiter string and
      • all object names that do not contain the specified delimiter.
Parameters:
delimiter - delimiter for list request.
